<ext_description linkend="Requirement_assignment_arm.Requirement_source">
A requirement_source relates a requirement (via the requirement_view_definition entity) to the data types representing the source of the requirement
<example>
The source of the requirement "the vehicle shall have a maximum power output of at least 150BHP" could be a document representing the findings of a
market survey of sports car buyers.
</example> 
</ext_description>
